Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.36,0:00:11.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用茶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,久違的溫泉讓我好好享受了一番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同感 料理也很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.42,0:00:26.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是托鶴屋學姐的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.29,0:00:28.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.17,0:00:33.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說回來 這裡是她親戚經營的旅館吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.01,0:00:35.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,確實在路上也遇到過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.05,0:00:40.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別看她那樣 其實好像是個大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.85,0:00:41.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.60,0:00:44.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說好安靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.06,0:00:49.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 可以說這個夜晚能讓人忘記平日的疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.61,0:00:53.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偶爾在這種能讓人靜下心來的地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.78,0:00:56.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古泉 鎖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.33,0:01:03.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.16,0:01:06.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夜晚才剛剛開始喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
