Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.55,0:02:42.51,Title - 3,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1312,880)\fad(695,695)}將那隻手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝比奈學姐她們怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.64,0:02:51.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝比奈學姐好像已經累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在在房間休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.69,0:02:55.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鶴屋學姐在陪她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.78,0:02:58.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,累的原因基本上都是洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請節哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.37,0:03:07.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,耶 Nice 古泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.29,0:03:15.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 撲克牌已經到手了 開始玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.67,0:03:21.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深夜撲克牌大賽 我在此宣佈正式開賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼宮 聲音太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在是晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.56,0:03:29.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回答只要一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.31,0:03:31.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼要玩什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都懂得規則的比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼大家知道Seven bridge嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.78,0:03:44.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Poker呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.87,0:03:45.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.28,0:03:46.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Page one呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道知道知道知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Rummy呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.92,0:03:53.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舉紅旗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.96,0:03:54.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.71,0:03:58.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒想到真的會舉起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 神經衰弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.51,0:04:09.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 這樣一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就決定是抽鬼牌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼最後會那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鬼牌靠運氣和生存方式來決定成敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼意思 大學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開始抽到鬼牌是靠運氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.54,0:04:36.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把鬼牌留在手中是生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,撲克牌可以說是人生的映射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不想贊同啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就從古泉開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.36,0:05:06.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,懲罰要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這個人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,懲罰就算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是挺有趣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有任何風險的遊戲一點也不刺激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣 有希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,懲罰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我覺得挺有趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.48,0:05:40.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要不太過火就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太過火啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,順便一問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有希所說的過火到底是哪種程度才算過火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.36,0:05:52.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了以後有所參考 我也很想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們兩個人 到此為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門困擾著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總而言之 第一次就去當跑腿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,輸的人就要去買吃的喝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼 那豈不是很無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要更加殘酷一點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然我是那麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.35,0:06:21.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一次就算是熱身 我就同意了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自然而然的氣氛不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無意間的幫助和無意間的感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.87,0:06:44.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,確實最近這兩個人的距離感縮小了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.63,0:06:49.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在人面前都這樣 要是在兩人獨處的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定會發生不得了的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有希 一開始就拿著的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼你知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都寫在臉上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼有希就去跑腿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.25,0:07:20.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.21,0:07:24.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.09,0:07:27.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等會等會 那懲罰不就沒有意義了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.39,0:07:36.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話是那樣 但是不能讓她一個人走夜路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了 朝倉也跟過來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就更完全談不上是懲罰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.07,0:07:49.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要買點心的話 我一個人也足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然我還是要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.76,0:08:17.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.93,0:08:24.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊路燈比較少 注意點腳下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.73,0:08:28.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來 手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣就不會摔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.14,0:09:06.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 給我水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來 請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.23,0:09:09.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.57,0:09:18.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼 喂 你到底在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不愧是涼子 這緊迫感真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.37,0:09:26.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然會這樣陷入妄想的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連我自己都不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 要是長門輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才的情況也是有可能的不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不 我要冷靜下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,湊成一對了 結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再怎麼想也是杞人憂天吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒牌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.48,0:09:54.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就決定涼子去當跑腿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 玩下一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噢 正如我意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.95,0:10:06.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實久瑠恢復過來了 於是我們過來玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有你們兩個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古泉又去了溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.38,0:10:19.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為被罰做了五十次下蹲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後剩下的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那邊睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.23,0:10:31.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉的生活很規律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.52,0:10:34.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一般這個時候都睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,春喵一整天跑來跑去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.03,0:10:42.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你們兩個就開始愉快地玩神經衰弱嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要說也應該說是寂寞地玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.29,0:10:50.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我就告訴你們兩個人一件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從這個旅館稍微往上登一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.96,0:10:57.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正好有一個可以看星星的展望台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.72,0:10:58.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.38,0:10:59.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.59,0:11:04.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來這裡本來也是想讓你們去那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.51,0:11:08.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那兩個人睡成那個樣子 也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有你們兩個人也好 去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.20,0:11:25.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.00,0:11:29.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是流了一身汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回去了還要泡一次溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.30,0:11:36.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是沒想到路這麼長 坡又這麼急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.89,0:11:49.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過錯還是錯在我們相信了鶴屋學姐的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.39,0:11:55.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走這麼黑的夜路果然有點怕怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.23,0:11:56.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以防萬一 要不我們牽著手走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不也可以認輸原路返回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.08,0:12:16.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我覺得應該可以再走一段路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難得都到這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 接著繼續前進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.72,0:12:28.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.85,0:12:32.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.85,0:12:36.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走累了 手上出了汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可不介意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.23,0:12:42.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？手上的汗是累了就出的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.21,0:12:56.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 應該要把手牽起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.25,0:13:00.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才剛睡醒 你真精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.46,0:13:05.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在說什麼啊 我們可是從背後守護長門會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼能沒羞沒臊的睡覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別這麼隨隨便便把我拉入會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是去看星星而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.73,0:13:17.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再說 我是看涼子寂寞才跟上來的 來感謝我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 跟上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恐龍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在玩什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難得來到這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.54,0:13:40.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玩一下有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來 涼子也來玩玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.05,0:13:50.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底他們變成什麼樣才能使你安心啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.93,0:13:51.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘴上說著要他們牽手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交往也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但又不想他們跨過那條界線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們要是交往的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.24,0:14:10.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我會很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.24,0:14:14.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是長門跟阿虛的關係越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.29,0:14:18.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就覺得長門跟我的距離越遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,僅僅是覺得寂寞跟不願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.84,0:14:34.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不是擔心 只是單純的嫉妒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.14,0:14:43.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼子 好像笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.52,0:14:49.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好壞 剛剛那情景應該用溫柔的話來安慰我才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.49,0:14:59.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,旁觀者看來你們的關繫好到都不知道在擔心什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.46,0:15:05.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我覺得他們倆的關係怎麼變也不會影響你們之間的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由我來保證 你就安心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.47,0:15:14.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的保證反而讓我不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.64,0:15:20.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是勉強算是好話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.52,0:15:21.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我僅僅是把你當笨蛋而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全沒有干讓你道謝的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.49,0:15:33.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 翼手龍 始祖鳥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我屁屁陷進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.42,0:15:52.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,橫穿肚子的大洞 看來很痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.15,0:16:13.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 生下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.62,0:16:27.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起雙冠龍 雖說脖子上有皺褶 讓人感覺會吐毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但實際上是否那樣也沒人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.71,0:16:31.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.88,0:16:33.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 沒在說那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？大家都在休息？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.80,0:16:45.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實玖瑠又暈過去了 我再背一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,背著朝比奈學姐走那山路？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然這人厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.18,0:17:20.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這確實是個美麗的風景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得好 鶴屋學姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能讓你們喜歡 我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來 我去叫在泡澡的古泉的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他說等一下會拿零食上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在泡澡的時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是不問下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能這麼容易看到星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宇宙船啊什麼的突然出來也不會覺得奇怪對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.88,0:17:49.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 有希是相信有宇宙人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開始天體觀測喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊對了 訊息 訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不我畫在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.59,0:18:00.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,訊息？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.97,0:18:02.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能寫的東西 能寫的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有沒有木棒之類的東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼都行 能在地上寫東西的就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.11,0:18:14.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛 涼子你們別發呆了 過來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有學姐跟實玖瑠也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 實玖瑠在那休息就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.58,0:18:25.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來來 我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.29,0:18:31.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家 久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah 古泉 辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,零食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要喝的可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那山路真險峻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你都大汗淋漓了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.06,0:18:47.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.19,0:18:51.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回去之後我想再泡次溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貼太近了 要泡腫你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.78,0:18:57.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣一來就全員集合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 大家都到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來我們來決定在這美麗的星空下該做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再這麼剝奪體力的話 會出現遇難者的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.25,0:19:12.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 想玩捉迷藏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.21,0:19:12.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,駁回！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.59,0:19:16.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,邊看星星邊聊天怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,駁回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}給我適可而止啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.47,0:19:21.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}因為那樣就太無聊了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古泉是捉迷藏派 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊哈哈哈哈 當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 實玖瑠 趕緊逃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實玖瑠衝刺！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是魔法什麼的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.89,0:20:07.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺能抓到 但又抓不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.11,0:20:23.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是時候回去了 一起吃零食吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.21,0:20:37.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.17,0:20:40.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,合宿結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.14,0:22:57.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣持續下雨 感覺很鬱悶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.85,0:22:58.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.81,0:22:59.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.89,0:23:02.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,梅雨過去了就是暑假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.31,0:23:03.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有好好的想過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.27,0:23:06.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想？想什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.44,0:23:07.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.32,0:23:10.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暑假開始之後 文藝社的活動也會休息了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.03,0:23:15.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼一來 跟阿虛見面的機會就沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.66,0:23:18.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 為了見阿虛要想好借口才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.83,0:23:21.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊 但是該怎麼樣的借口呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.67,0:23:23.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼都行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.34,0:23:25.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,例如天氣很熱 一起去游泳什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起來放煙火什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.59,0:23:28.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,認識阿虛才半年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.89,0:23:36.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還沒做過的事情還有很多對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.90,0:23:44.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天是特價日 我先去買東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.94,0:23:46.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 走好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.73,0:23:47.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我走了
